%E5%B1%95%E7%A4%BApdf"><span class="toc-text">6.7 展示pdf</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#6-8-%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E6%B1%87%E6%80%BB"><span class="toc-text">6.8 插件汇总</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#6-9-%E5%89%8D%E7%AB%AF%E7%A6%81%E6%AD%A2%E5%8F%B3%E9%94%AE%EF%BC%8CF12%EF%BC%8CF5"><span class="toc-text">6.9 前端禁止右键，F12，F5</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#6-10-%E6%98%9F%E7%A9%BA%E8%83%8C%E6%99%AF"><span class="toc-text">6.10 星空背景</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#6-11-%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%E6%9D%A1%E3%80%81%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%E6%9D%A1"><span class="toc-text">6.11 动态分类条、标签条</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#6-12-%E6%8F%90%E5%8F%96%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E8%89%B2%E5%B9%B6%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93%E9%A2%9C%E8%89%B2"><span class="toc-text">6.12 提取图片主题色并修改字体颜色</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#7-%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%E9%AD%94%E6%94%B9"><span class="toc-text">7. 高级魔改</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#7-1-Github-Calendar"><span class="toc-text">7.1 Github Calendar</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#7-2-%E9%A6%96%E9%A1%B5%E7%A3%81%E8%B4%B4"><span class="toc-text">7.2 首页磁贴</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#7-3-%E9%A6%96%E9%A1%B5%E7%BD%AE%E9%A1%B6%E8%BD%AE%E6%92%AD%E5%9B%BE"><span class="toc-text">7.3 首页置顶轮播图</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#7-4-%E5%8F%8B%E9%93%BE%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E5%9C%88"><span class="toc-text">7.4 友链朋友圈</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-5"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%9C%80%E5%90%8E%EF%BC%8C%E6%9C%AC%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0%E5%8E%9F%E5%88%9B%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85%E5%9D%87%E6%9D%A5%E8%87%AA%E